#. encoding=ASCII len_field=280
msgctxt "DT_Levels@e0@a85e"
msgid "After expanding into the Gas Giant Titania, we discovered that the rings of a nearby Ice Planet contain everything we need to expand and automate our water-to-oxygen pipeline.\r\n\r\nIf we hope to mass-produce explosives and weapons, this is going to have to be our next destination."
