#: DT_Levels export[0] offset=0xb827
#. encoding=ASCII len_field=237
msgctxt "DT_Levels@e0@b827"
msgid "We've still had <Bold>no contact</> from the mission sent to the <Bold>Lava Planet Cerberus</>, so we have no choice but to make sure that any future operations sent to this area can defend themselves against <Bold>hostile threats...</>"
