#: DT_Levels export[0] offset=0xd6b1
#. encoding=ASCII len_field=238
msgctxt "DT_Levels@e0@d6b1"
msgid "Its time to take the gloves off, Station Commander, and perform a <Bold>surgical strike</> with a task-force of powerful <Bold>military capital ships</> - we think the following will be sufficient to get the job done:\r\n\r\n{REQUIRED_SHIPS}"
