#: DT_Tutorials export[0] offset=0xb1
#. encoding=ASCII len_field=492
msgctxt "DT_Tutorials@e0@b1"
msgid "To build new modules on your station, enter <Bold>Build Mode</> using the Build option on the <Bold>Mode Bar</> at the bottom of the screen or press the <Bold>Build hotkey</>.\r\n\r\nChoose a <Bold>Build Category</> to see all available modules in that section, and then choose an option from the list to enter <Bold>Placing Mode</>.\r\n\r\nIf you have the required <Bold>parts</> in your <Bold>Drone's inventory</>, you can click to build, or <Bold>drag</> to automatically add <Bold>connectors</>."
msgstr ""

