#: DT_Tutorials export[0] offset=0x1c76
#. encoding=ASCII len_field=409
msgctxt "DT_Tutorials@e0@1c76"
msgid "To speed up resource collection you can now construct <Bold>Miners</> onto the <Bold>resource nodes</> you may find on larger asteroids.\r\n\r\nMiners can have other <Bold>station modules</> built onto them to create <Bold>sub-stations</> which can supply your main base with resources.\r\n\r\nLater in the game you will be able to automate moving resources between miners and your station using <Bold>Freighters</>."
msgstr ""

